      "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nI had tested patch set #7 (only the autoconf changes) on my local system, since it has a new autoconf version. If you don't object, I will resubmit that patch for this Change-Id, and you can add your portability fixes to a dependent patch.  Alternately, I can submit just the autoconf fixes to a separate change, and you can keep this patch for the portability fixes.",
